\n- Files read: 8 unique, 13 total reads (harness-run.md read 5 times, harness-run-dispatch.test.ts read 2 times)\n- Redundant operations: minimal\n\n### 16-5-rewrite-harness-run-verification-dispatch — verification (2026-03-28T11:05)\n\nNo issues reported. ALL_PASS (7/7 ACs).\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 15\n- By tool: Bash: 10, Read: 5, Grep: 2\n- Largest Bash outputs: `npm test` tail (~80 lines), `vitest --reporter=verbose` grep (~34 lines), `vitest --coverage` tail (~30 lines)\n- Files read: 3 unique, 5 total reads (harness-run.md read 3 times at different offsets)\n- Redundant operations: npm test run twice (could have captured in one call)\n\n### 16-6-update-create-story-tier-criteria — code review (2026-03-28T11:12)\n\n- **Bugs found:** 1 HIGH (AC2 test was false-pass risk — fixed by adding Given/When/Then format validation), 2 MEDIUM (assessed, no fix needed — fragile markers, semantic headings), 1 LOW (test count docs drift)\n- **Coverage gaps:** None.\n- **Items sent back for re-development:** None.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 19\n- By tool: Bash: 8, Read: 7, Edit: 2, Grep: 3, Glob: 1, Skill: 1\n- Files read: 8 unique, 10 total reads\n- Redundant operations: story test file run 3 times\n\n### 16-6-update-create-story-tier-criteria — verification (2026-03-28T11:21)\n\nNo issues reported. ALL_PASS (10/10 ACs). 5 pre-existing BATS failures (all_tasks_complete suite) unrelated.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 15\n- Files read: ~8 unique\n- Redundant operations: minimal\n\n### 16-7-update-knowledge-and-enforcement-docs — code review (2026-03-28T11:27)\n\n- **Bugs found:** 0 HIGH, 4 MEDIUM (all fixed — missing escalate tier test, weak AC8 assertions, silent empty-string fallback in section extraction x2), 2 LOW (not fixed — legacy terms in patches/AGENTS.md, patches/retro/enforcement.md, src/templates/verify-prompt.ts — all out of story scope)\n- **Coverage gaps:** None. All 158 files above 80% floor, 96.85% overall.\n- **Architecture concerns:** None.\n- **Items sent back for re-development:** None.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 22\n- By tool: Bash: 7, Read: 9, Edit: 4, Grep: 8, Glob: 1, Skill: 1\n- Largest Bash outputs: `git diff --name-only` (~20 lines), `npx vitest run` (~15 lines), `npx codeharness coverage` (~5 lines)\n- Files read: 10 unique, 11 total reads\n- Redundant operations: One redundant story file read, two grep passes for black.box could have been combined\n\n### 16-7-update-knowledge-and-enforcement-docs — verification (2026-03-28T11:32)\n\nNo issues reported. ALL_PASS (12/12 ACs).\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 16\n- By tool: Bash: 7, Read: 2, Grep: 10\n- Largest Bash outputs: `npm test` (~50 lines), `npx vitest run` (~15 lines), `ls verification/` (~100 lines)\n- Files read: 2 unique, 2 total reads\n- Redundant operations: npm test run twice (once truncated, once via vitest for cleaner output)\n\n### 16-8-update-all-tests — code review (2026-03-28T11:39)\n\n- **Bugs found:** None.\n- **Code quality issues (LOW, not fixed):** classifyTier barrel re-export not tested through index.ts; story line references will drift; no explicit runtime>test priority test in classifyTier.\n- **Coverage gaps:** None. 96.85% overall, all 158 files above 80%.\n- **Items sent back for re-development:** None.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 18\n- By tool: Bash: 3, Read: 11, Grep: 2, Glob: 4, Skill: 1\n- Largest Bash outputs: `npx vitest run` (~30 lines), `codeharness coverage` (~4 lines), `git diff --name-only` (~5 lines)\n- Files read: 14 unique, 14 total reads\n- Redundant operations: None\n\n### 16-8-update-all-tests — verification (2026-03-28T11:43)\n\nNo issues reported. ALL_PASS (12/12 ACs). Proof document updated from 4015→4020 test count.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 14\n- By tool: Bash: 7, Read: 6, Edit: 3\n- Largest Bash outputs: `npm test` (~40 lines), BATS test tail (~40 lines), `npx codeharness coverage` (~4 lines)\n- Files read: 7 unique, 7 total reads\n- Redundant operations: npm test run twice (full + grep-filtered for summary)\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":1,"oldLines":5,"newStart":1,"newLines":15,"lines":[" # Session Issues Log — 2026-03-28"," ","+### 16-7-update-knowledge-and-enforcement-docs — code review (2026-03-28T13:05)","+","+None. Re-review confirmed 0 issues, 12/12 ACs validated, 96.85% coverage.","+","+## Token Report","+- Total tool calls: 15","+- By tool: Bash: 4, Read: 7, Grep: 4, Skill: 1, Glob: 1","+- Files read: 9 unique, 9 total reads","+- Redundant operations: none","+"," ### 16-5-rewrite-harness-run-verification-dispatch — code review (2026-03-28T10:55)"," "," - **Bugs found:** 0 HIGH, 3 MEDIUM (all fixed — indexOf guard, DRY violation, fragile section coupling), 2 LOW (not fixed — section ordering, string-matching test brittleness)"]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false}}
