n that caused re-work\n6. **Lessons learned** — patterns to repeat or avoid\n7. **Action items** — concrete next steps\n\nWrite the retrospective to _bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/session-retro-2026-03-28.md. Since a session retro for today already exists, append to it with a `---` separator and timestamp.\n\nDo NOT ask the user any questions — proceed autonomously.\nDo NOT run git commit. Do NOT run git add. Do NOT modify sprint-status.yaml.","uuid":"7d99e9a4-9505-4cc3-8fd8-94193eb6cccd","session_id":"0e0ced21-c7cd-411a-a5de-15cffee11899"}
