{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01R7Ju5YekBooPaCY8m3WqtD","type":"tool_result","content":"  5500→3. **Retro file rotation is overdue.** At 285KB, the retro file cannot be read in full by tools. Archive per-sprint or impose a size cap.\n  5501→4. **Subagent prompt optimization pays off.** The `npm test` double-run pattern in verification subagents is a simple prompt fix worth ~$1.50/story.\n  5502→\n  5503→### 7. Action Items\n  5504→\n  5505→#### Immediate (before next session)\n  5506→\n  5507→| # | Action | Owner |\n  5508→|---|--------|-------|\n  5509→| 1 | Add monotonic status guard to Ralph: never revert a `done` story to any earlier status | ralph/ |\n  5510→| 2 | Add sprint-complete early exit: if `done === total`, skip all subagent spawning | ralph/ |\n  5511→\n  5512→#### Fix Soon (next sprint)\n  5513→\n  5514→| # | Action | Owner |\n  5515→|---|--------|-------|\n  5516→| 3 | Rotate retro files — archive this 285KB file and start fresh | harness tooling |\n  5517→| 4 | Add per-session cost delta tracking to `codeharness stats` | codeharness CLI |\n  5518→| 5 | Fix `npm test` double-run pattern in verification prompts | verification prompts |\n  5519→\n  5520→#### Backlog\n  5521→\n  5522→| # | Action | Owner |\n  5523→|---|--------|-------|\n  5524→| 6 | Clean up `1-1-foo` phantom story ($24.35 in cost tracking) | state management |\n  5525→| 7 | Fix 5 pre-existing BATS failures in `all_tasks_complete` suite | tests |\n  5526→| 8 | Address LOW-priority code review items deferred from epic 16 | tech debt |\n  5527→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01AW6v7ayRdwjRSfk21TWwfE","session_id":"0e0ced21-c7cd-411a-a5de-15cffee11899","uuid":"3cc49311-1c84-4c7e-8698-855ee6f2ffed","timestamp":"2026-03-28T13:22:10.421Z"}
